-captain|third-captain]]| }}\n{{football squad player|no=19|nat=GER|pos=MF|name=[[Leroy San\u00e9]]}}\n{{football squad mid}}\n{{football squad player|no=20|nat=POR|pos=MF|name=[[Bernardo Silva]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=21|nat=ESP|pos=MF|name=[[David Silva]] |other=[[Captain (association football)|captain]]| }}\n{{football squad player|no=22|nat=FRA|pos=DF|name=[[Benjamin Mendy]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=25|nat=BRA|pos=MF|name=[[Fernandinho (footballer, born May 1985)|Fernandinho]] |other=[[Captain (association football)#Vice-captain|vice-captain]]| }}\n{{football squad player|no=26|nat=ALG|pos=MF|name=[[Riyad Mahrez]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=27|nat=POR|pos=DF|name=[[Jo\u00e3o Cancelo]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=30|nat=ARG|pos=DF|name=[[Nicol\u00e1s Otamendi]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=31|nat=BRA|pos=GK|name=[[Ederson (footballer, born 1993)|Ederson]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=33|nat=ENG|pos=GK|name=[[Scott Carson]]|other=on loan from [[Derby County F.C.|Derby County]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=47|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Phil Foden]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=50|pos=DF|nat=ESP|name=[[Eric Garc\u00eda (footballer, born 2001)|Eric Garc\u00eda]]|other=}}\n{{football squad end}}\n\n==== Out on loan ====\nThe following players have previously made a league or cup appearance for Manchester City and are currently on loan at other teams:\n\n{{football squad start}}\n{{football squad player|no=12|nat=ESP|pos=DF|name=[[Angeli\u00f1o]]|other=at [[RB Leipzig]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{football squad player|no=24|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Tosin Adarabioyo]]|other=at [[Blackburn Rovers F.C.|Blackburn Rovers]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref name=\"ESPN FC\">{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.us/english-fa-cup/story/2812117/manchester-city-give-five-young-players-debuts-at-chelsea|title=Man City give five young players debuts in FA Cup game at Chelsea|publisher=ESPN FC|date=21 February 2016|accessdate=24 August 2016}}</ref>\n{{football squad player|no=34|nat=NED|pos=DF|name=[[Philippe Sandler]]|other=at [[R.S.C. Anderlecht|Anderlecht]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{football squad player|no=43 |nat=GER|pos=FW|name=[[Lukas Nmecha]]|other=at [[Middlesbrough F.C.|Middlesbrough]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{football squad mid}}\n{{football squad player|no=49 |nat=KVX|pos=GK|name=[[Arijanet Muric]]|other=at [[Nottingham Forest F.C.|Nottingham Forest]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref name=\"numbers\">{{cite web |title=Man City squad numbers for 2017/18 season |url=https://www.mancity.com/news/first%20team/first%20team%20news/2017/august/man%20city%20squad%20numbers%201718%20season |publisher=Manchester City F.C. |accessdate=23 July 2018}}</ref>\n{{football squad player|no=75|nat=ESP|pos=MF|name=[[Aleix Garc\u00eda]]|other=at [[Royal Excel Mouscron]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref name=\"ESPN FC\"/>\n{{football squad player|no= 81|pos=MF|nat=FRA|name=[[Claudio Gomes]]|other=at [[PSV Eindhoven]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref name=\"CommShield\">{{cite web |last1=Bevan |first1=Chris |title=Community Shield: Chelsea 0\u20132 Manchester City \u2013 Sergio Aguero scores twice |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44995783 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=5 August 2018}}</ref>\n{{football squad player|no=\u2014 |nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Patrick Roberts]]|other=at [[Middlesbrough F.C.|Middlesbrough]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{football squad end}}\n\n==== Other players with first-team appearances ====\n{{Main|Manchester City F.C. EDS and Academy}}\t\n{{football squad start|nat=|pos=|other=|no=|name=}}\t\n{{fs player|no= 61|pos=MF|nat=ENG|name=[[Felix Nmecha]]}}<ref name=\"BMC\">{{cite web |title=Burton v Man City |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/46839107 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=23 January 2019}}</ref>\n{{fs player|no= 69|pos=MF|nat=ENG|name=[[Tommy Doyle (footballer, born 2001)|Tommy Doyle]]}}\n{{football squad mid}}\n{{fs player|no= 78|pos=DF|nat=ENG|name=[[Taylor Harwood-Bellis]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=82|pos=MF|nat=ESP|name=[[Adri\u00e1n Bernab\u00e9]]|other=}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mancity.com/news/first-team/match-report/2018/september/oxford-united-v-man-city-carabao-cup-round-3-match-report|title=Oxford United v Manchester City Match Report|work=Manchester City F.C. |date=25 September 2018 |accessdate=22 October 2018 |author=David Clayton}}</ref>\n\n{{football squad end|nat=|pos=|other=|no=|name=}}\n\n=== Retired numbers ===\n{{see also|List of retired numbers in association football}}\nSince 2003, Manchester City have not issued the squad number 23. It was [[Retired numbers in association football|retired]] in memory of [[Marc-Vivien Fo\u00e9]], who was on loan to the club from [[Olympique Lyonnais|Lyon]] at the time of his death on the field of play while playing for [[Cameroon national football team|Cameroon]] in the [[2003 FIFA Confederations Cup]].<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/3026212.stm |title=Man City retire number 23 shirt |publisher=BBC Sport |date=27 June 2003 |accessdate=22 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n{{football squad start}}\n{{football squad player|no=23|pos=MF|nat=CMR|name=[[Marc-Vivien Fo\u00e9]]|other=2002\u201303) \u2013 posthumous honour}}\n{{football squad end}}\n\n=== Player of the Year ===\n{|\n|width=\"1\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n{| class=\"toccolours\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:silver;\"|Year!! style=\"background:silver;\"|Winner\n|-\n|1985\u201386||{{flagicon|England}} [[Kenny Clements]]\n|-\n|1986\u201387||{{flagicon|Scotland}} [[Neil McNab]]\n|-\n|1987\u201388||{{flagicon|England}} [[Steve Redmond]]\n|-\n|1988\u201389||{{flagicon|Scotland}} [[Neil McNab]]\n|-\n|1989\u201390||{{flagicon|Scotland}} [[Colin Hendry]]\n|-\n|1990\u201391||{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Niall Quinn]]\n|-\n|1991\u201392||{{flagicon|England}} [[Tony Coton]]\n|-\n|1992\u201393||{{flagicon|England}} [[Garry Flitcroft]]\n|-\n|1993\u201394||{{flagicon|England}} [[Tony Coton]]\n|-\n|1994\u201395||{{flagicon|East Germany}} [[Uwe R\u00f6sler]]\n|}\n|width=\"1\"|&nbsp;\n|val