966\u20131979\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | 2007\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Billy Meredith]]            || [[Forward (association football)|FW]] ([[outside right]])\n| player || 1894\u20131906, 1921\u20131924\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Mark Hughes]]               || [[Forward (association football)|FW]]\n| manager || 2008\u20132009\n|-\n! 2009\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Frank Swift]]               || [[Goalkeeper (association football)|GK]]\n| player || 1933\u20131949\n|-\n! 2010\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Francis Lee]]               || [[Forward (association football)|FW]]\n| player || 1967\u20131974\n|-\n! 2013\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mike Summerbee]]            || [[Forward (association football)|FW]]\n| player || 1965\u20131975\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | 2014\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Trevor Francis]]            || [[Forward (association football)|FW]]\n| player || 1981\u20131982\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Patrick Vieira]]               || [[Midfielder|MF]]\n| player and coach || 2010\u20132015\n|-\n! 2015\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Stuart Pearce]]            || [[Defender (association football)|DF]]\n| player and manager || 2001\u20132002, 2005\u20132007\n|-\n! 2016\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[David Seaman]]            || [[Goalkeeper (association football)|GK]]\n| player || 2003\u20132004\n|-\n| style=\"width:90px;\"|\n! colspan=\"4\" | Managers with Manchester City backgrounds inducted to date\n|-\n! 2002\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Matt Busby|Sir Matt Busby]], [[CBE]], [[KCSG]]\n| [[Forward (association football)|FW]] ([[inside right]]) / <br> [[Defensive midfielder|MF]] ([[right half]])\n| player || 1928\u20131936\n|-\n! 2004\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Don Revie]], [[OBE]]        || [[Forward (association foot